summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2533, for the improvement of 9th Avenue Northeast from East 63rd Street to East 65th Street and East 64th Street from 8th Avenue Northeast to 10th Avenue Northeast, all in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, all in accordance with Majority Petition No. 47067, under Ordinance No. 29415 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
